136
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:39,800
Mo...

137
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:51,840
Mother,

138
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:53,520
I'm sorry for being late.

139
00:11:53,580 --> 00:11:56,700
