140
00:12:03,660 --> 00:12:05,000
This is...

141
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,720
Seeing your mother,

142
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,560
aren't you surprised?

143
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,360
Yin Ruoshui.

